Jacqueline B. Marcus, MS, RD, LD, CNS, FADA is President/Owner of Jacqueline B. Marcus &amp; Associates, a multi-service food and nutrition consulting firm in Northfield, Illinois, USA. She holds a Bachelor of Science degree in Family, Consumer, and Nutrition Sciences, and a Master of Science degree in Food and Nutrition from Northern Illinois University.
